    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a benchmark of mechanical purity. This example features the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing high-pressure double-VANOS and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The suspension remains tight with factory-spec bushings and dampers, maintaining original kinematics. This is a collector-grade specimen with flawless paint depth and a showroom-correct interior, free of the typical subframe or rod bearing concerns.",
